      .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
        h1 <strong>Priest</strong>, free online <strong>converter and formatter</strong>
        p.
          My friend, before we proceed — let me ask you three questions of utmost importance.
        p.
          Do you believe in <strong>CoffeeScript</strong>, Almighty and Supreme?
        p.
          Do you believe in <strong>Stylus</strong>, Heightened and Blissful?
        p.
          Do you believe in <strong>Jade</strong>, Immaculate and Pure?
        p.
          If your eyes widen, your breath quickens, your heart hastens upon hearing these names — advance bravely, for I am destined to be revealed before the open-minded.
        p.
          Behold the Universal Converter. It divinely translates any code into holy scripture.
        .well.converter
          .input
            if isWebkit
              p
                | Convert whole directory:
                | &nbsp;
                input.files(type="file" name="dir" directory webkitdirectory mozdirectory)
            p
              | Convert files:
              | &nbsp;
              input.files(type="file" name="files[]" multiple)
            .errors
              each errors
                .alert.alert-danger.fade.in
                  button.close(type='button', data-dismiss='alert', aria-hidden='true') ×
                  p #{.}
            textarea(placeholder="Convert code")
            p * Orthodox encoding of "UTF-8" assumed
            .alert.alert-success
              strong Your data is safe, my friend.
              | &nbsp;
              | Whatever you convert stays inside your browser.
        h2 Rejoice with brethren
